<h2 id="meeting-time">Meeting Time</h2>

<p>The SSWG meets biweekly on Wednesday at 2:00PM PT (USA Pacific). The meetings take place in the weeks with the <a href="http://www.whatweekisit.org">odd week numbers</a>.</p>
